{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Node.nextSibling","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><em><code>nextSibling</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"allgemein","title":"Allgemein","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Gibt den Datenknoten zurück, der entsprechend der <code>childNodes</code>-Liste des Elternelements direkt auf den gegebenen Datenknoten folgt. Falls der übergebene Knoten bereits der letzte dieser Liste ist, wird <code>null</code> zurückgegeben.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">nextNode = node.nextSibling;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiele","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Folgendes HTML-Dokument ist gegeben:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Das ist eine DIV-Box<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hier steht Text!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Mit folgendem Code kann der Name des Geschwisterelements der DIV-Box ermittelt werden:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Diese Variable speichert eine Referenz auf das Erste Element, das &lt;body&gt; enthält, also die DIV-Box</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Nun ermitteln wir das folgende Element</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> folgeElement <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nextSibling<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// Ausgabe des nodeNames</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>folgeElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Erläuterung:</strong></p>\n<p>Die Variable <code><var>element</var></code> enthält das erste Kindelement des <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>-Tags, also die <code>DIV</code>-Box.<br>\n <code><var>folgeElement</var></code> speichert den ersten Geschwisterknoten der DIV-Box. In diesem Fall ist das ein Textknoten der einen Zeilenvorschub und vier Leerzeichen enthält, die sich in dem HTML-Dokument zwischen dem <code>&gt;</code> der DIV-Box und dem <code>&lt;</code> des <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> befinden. Das <code>alert()</code>-Fenster gibt somit <code>#text</code> aus.</p>\n<p>Folgendermaßen können alle nachfolgenden Geschwisterknoten ermittelt werden:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> liste <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nextSibling<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> liste<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>liste<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nextSibling<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Das Skript erzeugt ein Array <code>liste</code> mit folgendem Inhalt:</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">Array[3]\n  0: Text\n  1: HTMLParagraphElement\n  2: Text\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"anmerkungen","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Am obigen Beispiel lässt sich klar erkennen, dass einige Male ein <code>#text</code>-Knoten im Index auftaucht. Das kommt immer dann vor, wenn sich zwischen den Elementen Whitespace befindet. Da die Eigenschaft <code>nextSibling</code> auch Textknoten berücksichtigt, landet dieser Whitespace letztendlich als Solcher im Index. Falls dies nicht erwünscht ist, sollten Sie statt <code>nextSibling</code> die Eigenschaft <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/nextElementSibling\"><code>Element.nextElementSibling</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> verwenden</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#attribute-nextSibling\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core: nextSibling</a>&nbsp;(en)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-6AC54C2F\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: nextSibling</a>&nbsp;(en)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Element.nextElementSibling\" title=\"En/DOM/Element.nextElementSibling\">Element.nextElementSibling</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Gibt den Datenknoten zurück, der entsprechend der childNodes-Liste des Elternelements direkt auf den gegebenen Datenknoten folgt. Falls der übergebene Knoten bereits der letzte dieser Liste ist, wird null zurückgegeben.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.nextSibling","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.nextSibling","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.nextSibling","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/nextsibling","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/nextsibling/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling","title":"Node.nextSibling"}],"pageTitle":"Node.nextSibling - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}